They put the red
and the chartreuse,

00:20:53.270 --> 00:20:55.670
and that's what's making
the room super fun.

00:20:55.670 --> 00:20:57.910
And so when you're
making pictures,

00:20:57.910 --> 00:21:00.100
you have to do that also.

00:21:00.100 --> 00:21:03.670
And see how we used the pops
of color for the plates.

