00:21:22.390 --> 00:21:24.760
and a brown.

00:21:24.760 --> 00:21:27.527
It gives that sort of
mid-century modern vibe, which

00:21:27.527 --> 00:21:29.110
doesn't really go
in my house, but you

00:21:29.110 --> 00:21:32.810
can sort of mix everything
together and make it look good.

00:21:32.810 --> 00:21:34.570
But then we used the
pop of the colors

00:21:34.570 --> 00:21:36.910
of the chairs and
the plates to make

00:21:36.910 --> 00:21:38.950
the picture look interesting.

00:21:38.950 --> 00:21:44.650
Here what we've done
