Here is a different
kind of spacing.

00:22:07.630 --> 00:22:12.420
And here is a different
kind of spacing.

00:22:12.420 --> 00:22:16.480
So I started with one stripe
and then kept filling the holes.

00:22:16.480 --> 00:22:18.310
So a lot of this
is playing around.

00:22:18.310 --> 00:22:22.750
Not everything is successful,
but paint is cheap.

00:22:22.750 --> 00:22:25.900
And you can just
slap it on the wall.

00:22:25.900 --> 00:22:27.790
You don't like it,
just change it.

